Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 五百祗先生 到秋天了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有秋天的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?秋天的氣味?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點塵土味 有點陽光味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點涼涼的又好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是種讓人感覺很懷念的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有記憶了還知道秋天的氣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:40.34,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:35.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:35.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:43.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:43.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:00.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:00.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:07.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:07.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:10.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:10.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:18.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:18.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:24.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:24.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:41.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:41.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

